MARS MRT: Day-Level Analyses

June 11, 2024

  • 1 Marginal association between engagement in self-regulatory strategies and cigarette use on current day
  • 2 Time-varying association between engagement in self-regulatory strategies and cigarette use on current day
  • 3 Marginal association between engagement in self-regulatory strategies and cigarette use on next day
  • 4 Time-varying association between engagement in self-regulatory strategies and next day cigarette use

1 Marginal association between engagement in self-regulatory strategies and cigarette use on current day

\[ \mathrm{logit} Pr \left( S_{i,d} = 1 \Bigg| \sum_{b = 1}^6 I_{i, d, b} \geq 1 \right) = \beta_0 + \beta_1 X_{i,d} \]

2 Time-varying association between engagement in self-regulatory strategies and cigarette use on current day

\[ \text{logit} Pr\left(\text{ANY CIGARETTE USE}_{i} \left(t_{i,j} \right) = 1\right)= \beta_0 \left(t_{i,j}\right) + \beta_1 \left(t_{i,j}\right) \text{NO. OF TIMES ENGAGED} \left(t_{i,j}\right) \]

\[ E\left(\text{NO. OF CIGARETTES SMOKED}_{i} \left(t_{i,j} \right) = 1\right)= \beta_0 \left(t_{i,j}\right) + \beta_1 \left(t_{i,j}\right) \text{NO. OF TIMES ENGAGED} \left(t_{i,j}\right) \]

3 Marginal association between engagement in self-regulatory strategies and cigarette use on next day

\[ \mathrm{logit} Pr \left( S_{i,d + 1} = 1 \Bigg| \left\{\sum_{b = 1}^6 I_{i,d, b} \geq 1\right\} \cap \left\{\sum_{b = 1}^6 I_{i,d+1, b} \geq 1\right\} \right) = \beta_0 + \beta_1 S_{i,d} + \beta_2 X_{i,d} \]

4 Time-varying association between engagement in self-regulatory strategies and next day cigarette use

\[ \text{logit} Pr\left(\text{ANY CIGARETTE USE}_{i} \left(t_{i,j+1} \right) = 1\right)= \beta_0 \left(t_{i,j}\right) + \beta_1 \left(t_{i,j}\right) \text{ANY CIGARETTE USE}_{i} \left(t_{i,j}\right) + \beta_2 \left(t_{i,j}\right) \text{NO. OF TIMES ENGAGED} \left(t_{i,j}\right) \]

\[ E\left(\text{NO. OF CIGARETTES SMOKED}_{i} \left(t_{i,j+1} \right) = 1\right)= \beta_0 \left(t_{i,j}\right) + \beta_1 \left(t_{i,j}\right) \text{ANY CIGARETTE USE}_{i} \left(t_{i,j}\right) + \beta_2 \left(t_{i,j}\right) \text{NO. OF TIMES ENGAGED} \left(t_{i,j}\right) \]
